quizes.title: What is React
quizes.description: React, also known as React.js or ReactJS, is a free and open-source front-end JavaScript library for building user interfaces (UIs). It is maintained by Meta (formerly Facebook) and a community of individual developers and companies UPDATED

quizes.title: what is vite
quizes.description: Vite is a build tool and development server designed for modern web development, emphasizing speed and a streamlined developer experience. It leverages native ES modules during development and uses Rollup for production builds. This approach results in faster server startup and module replacement compared to traditional bundlers like Webpack.
